<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;" charset="utf-8" >
    <meta name="viewport" charset="UTF-8" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Goby</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/clearstyle.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/global.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/build.css">
  </head>
  <body data-page="build">
    <!-- <p>This page will be built out later on, but for now it'll just have an input that lets you see whether a channel has goby set up, and sends you to the appropriate page from there</p> -->
    <div id="title-bar" class="prose">
      <div class="channel-picked">
        <p>Are.na / <span id="username"></span> / <span class="emphasis" id="channel-name"></span></p>
        <button type="button" name="button" id="pick-different">Pick a different channel</button>

      </div>
      <div class="pick-channel flex-row input-url">
        <input type="text" name="" value="" placeholder="https://are.na/<username-slug>/<channel-slug>">
        <button type="button" name="button" id="initiate-search">find channel</button>
      </div>

    </div>
    <div class="columns">
        <form class="input prose">
          <p>Goby works by storing and modifying a single text block at the bottom of a channel called <i>goby.json</i>. This block contains all your metadata in JSON format. Here's <a href="https://www.are.na/block/12011259" target="_blank">an example</a>.</p>
          <p>This page generates a new <i>goby.json</i> for your channel, so that you can view it in the Goby editor.</p>
          <p id="commentary">
            <span class="a">Goby is not yet installed in this channel. Press the button below to start the building process.</span>
            <span class="b">Goby is not yet installed in this channel. You can't install it because you're not the channel owner.</span>
            <span class="c">Goby is not yet installed in this channel. You'll need to <button type="button" name="button" class="open-login">log in</button> before you can install it.</span>
            <button type="button" name="button" id="install">Install goby in this channel</button>
          </p>


        </form>
        <div class="output">
          <div id="terminal" class="prose">

          </div>
          <label>Build log</label>
        </div>
    </div>
    {% include 'login.html' %}
    {% include 'icons.html' %}

    <!-- <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js" charset="utf-8"></script> -->
    <script src="../../js/d3.min.js" defer></script>
    <script src="../../js/global.js" charset="utf-8" defer></script>
    <script src="../../js/build.js" charset="utf-8" defer></script>
  </body>
</html>
